      "comment": "MYSTIC PHARAOH (8) box seated before sticking on well to finish 3.5 lengths away in third (30.45) at Sandown in a Maiden over 515m. Capable of going well again. DIMORA BIG BOY (7) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 7th at Warrnambool following on from a third place finish (22.82) there the start prior. Comes out of a hot form race last start. One of the main contenders. DIMORA PATCH (1) has an honest record despite remaining a maiden and overdue for a win, having placed six of 18 career runs. Cannot be taken lightly. THUNDERING THEO (2) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.",
